<item>
            <title>[LU-6431] do not call blocking ops when !TASK_RUNNING</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6431</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;New upstream kernels added additional checking to CONFIG_DEBUG_ATOMIC__SLEEP to ensure no blocking calls are made while in not RUNNIG state,as otherwise the state could be lost.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For us offenders are in __l_wait_event for callbacks,&lt;br/&gt;
in libcfs_debug_dumplog and in libcfs_sock_accept&lt;/p&gt;</description>
